{
  "texts": [
    "In the following sub-sections, I unpack five central points of the resistance undertook by MOSACAT and the Council.",
    "I include the term 'elemental' in them since, even if this might sound repetitive, each point mobilises different articulations of this term.",
    "An elemental ethics begins by proactively situating water as the central concern for local communities.",
    "While the construction of a data centre can bring about different issues, MOSACAT decided to focus its struggle on water rights after it heard about Google's project.",
    "The reason for this choice became clear to me when I asked activists whether they would be interested in forging alliances with digital rights groups already fighting against Google and other big tech companies."
  ]
}